p: In this study, a total of 34 metabolites of AMF were found. Metabolites were mainly distributed in feces, including 34 metabolites (M1â€“M34), and 3 metabolites were in urine (M4, M7, and M17). No metabolite of AMF was found in bile or plasma. The result was shown in Figures 7 and 8 and Table 3.
